<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Arena for Pvp that is game sponsered.</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Druez the Quick">Druez the Quick</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 7:04 a.m. 14/2/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Arena for Pvp that is game sponsered.<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>I'm telling you guys if you could put this into your game and support it the way it should be, it would be a big selling point. Build an arena have, lets say the top 20 pvp players listed on the boards. Have people have to pay a fee to enter the ladder. Once in the ladder, keep track of their win and loss record and their place on ladder. Have it set up by npc's so only 2 people can go into arena at one time. Make a betting window so people who are watching can place bets on the outcome of the fight. Hold grand tournaments and the like. If you can do this it will make alot of people want to be pvp +.

<BR>I mean think about the fun this could be. If you like my idea, I can write a fag or a proposel and put it on my website. I have suggested this to the gms at uo for a long time. I mean they have an arena and still can't get it done. There are player sponsered fight nights all the time, but they are usually mismanaged and not well done. Just a thought.
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
